[color=red][size=18]Spec Racer Ford Challenge Series @ [b] Mid-Ohio Sports Car Course - Full[/b]
Week 10 of 12 - 2019 Season 2 [/size][/color]
Race Distance: [b]15 laps[/b], approximately 25 minutes
World Record lap time: [b]1:35.832[/b] by Charlie Summers
(n.b. random/dynamic weather impacts lap times greatly)

For week 10 we travel to Mid-Ohio Sports Car Course. This track is home to many racing events including the real-life SRF SCCA runoffs  and provides excellent racing. With several overtaking opportunities and the challenging 'Madness' section winding through the mid-half of the lap, battles are fierce here, with attempted passes often resulting in half a lap or more of side-by-side action.

Target "planned" SoF race is usually 20:45 GMT Sunday, immediately following the Weekend Warriors league race.

[img]http://members.iracing.com/jforum/posts/downloadAttach/2363181.page[/img]

